I shouldn't have made you
my bodyguard at first.

53
00:03:49,200 --> 00:03:50,440
I want to make a deal with you.

54
00:03:51,080 --> 00:03:52,680
I can help you
reclaim the Lin Corporation.

55
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:54,080
(After it's done,)

56
